call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Curry's (DAL) jump shot attempt goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Thunder.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Williams (OKC).

As Williams (OKC) pursues the rebound, his left arm makes contact with Lively II's (DAL) face, which is marginal. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
